      "title": "The Trust Sandwich",
      "description": "## Trust Sandwich Architecture\n\nOur pipeline separates concerns into three trust layers:\n- **AI Layer** — LLM-powered nodes that handle fuzzy parsing (varied PDF formats)\n- **Deterministic Layer** — Pure Python math that *cannot* hallucinate\n- **Human Layer** — HITL veto gate when confidence drops below 80%\n\n![Trust Sandwich Architecture](.tours/images/trust-sandwich.png)",
